 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bf40c262d40>([-89])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bf40c262d40> = [[1, -89], [1, -89, 1], [-89], [-89, 1], [1, -89], [1, -89, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bf40c262d40>([1, -89])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bf40c262d40> = [[1, -89], [1, -89, 1], [-89], [-89, 1], [1, -89], [1, -89, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bf40c262d40>([-89, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bf40c262d40> = [[1, -89], [1, -89, 1], [-89], [-89, 1], [1, -89], [1, -89, 1], ...].count
